query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS email_events (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  emailLogId INT,
  resendEmailId VARCHAR(255),
  eventType ENUM('email.sent', 'email.delivered', 'email.delivery_delayed', 'email.bounced', 'email.complained', 'email.opened', 'email.clicked') NOT NULL,
  recipientEmail VARCHAR(320) NOT NULL,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  metadata JSON,
  rawPayload JSON,
  processedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  INDEX idx_emailLogId (emailLogId),
  INDEX idx_resendEmailId (resendEmailId),
  INDEX idx_eventType (eventType),
  INDEX idx_recipientEmail (recipientEmail)
)
